cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

The paper proposes a novel recurrent neural network model for hyperspectral image classification, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) domains. The use of a new activation function and modified gated recurrent unit also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper deals with data analysis and classification, which could also fit under information retrieval (cs.IR).
